column5: GOT OUT ON THE WATER AT 7AM THIS MORN TILL 6PM!! PRETTY MUCH COVERED THE WHOLE LAKE AND ONLY GOT 1 PERCH AND 1 NICE BASS!! TALK TO A BASS MASTER I KNOW AND HE SAID EVERY YR AT THIS TIME THEY SEEM TO SHUT DOWN!!! SO MAYBE A NEW LAKE NEXT OUTING IS NEEDED  LOL! TODAY OFF AND WORK TOMOR PAVING THE DVP!! WAVE HI AND SWEAR AT ME (MOST DO) CAUSE WERE CAUSING TRAFFIC JAMS  LOL  sorry about the bad quality on the shot(he dont really know how to use a digi  lol)

At least the weather treated you nicely out on the lake today.   Going to be fantastic weather to work on the dvp.  Can you please smooth out the one bump that spills coffee all over me every morning on my way to work?  I'm running out of shirts!  Hehe.  You guys do a good job.  Nice bass btw.
too bad about the tough fishing but at least you got out.
NICE BASS I SEE THE CAPS LOCK BUTTON MUST BE STCK ON YOUR PC AGAIN LOL
Got out on Simcoe today, same thing.  Had a follow by a small pike and that is it.
didn't know you fished anything but bows?
